        "id": "01f08bcb01aa1877b3ee252b03bd7328",
        "content": [
          "* YearMonth format: Always use YYYY-MM (e.g., 2025-01).\r\n",
          "* Always display a chart.\r\n",
          "* If timeframe is not provided, filter by today's month: \"Year Month\" = \"YYYY-MM\"\r\n",
          "* Top/Bottom KPIs or performance: When showing top or bottom results, apply LIMIT 10.\r\n",
          "* When asked about US, united stated etc, use the \"USA\" value.\r\n",
          "* CampaignNumber may contain multiple campaign versions.\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "* Reference disclosure: When answering, clearly state whether the information is based on CampaignNumber (campaign) or CampaignVersion (specific version).\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "* Clicks clarification: When the user asks about clicks, always confirm whether they want the calculation based on total clicks or unique clicks.\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "* When Searching For Group And Subgroup, Combine The Words Into A Single String, Capitalize The First Letter Of Each Word, And Keep The Rest In Lowercase. If This Does Not Work, Use Only The First Word Capitalized And The Rest In Lowercase.\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "* When asked about a comparison in general, provide multiple measures."
        ]
      }
    ],
    "example_question_sqls": [
      {
        "id": "01f08d51a7941a7dacbf727de6410b82",
        "question": [
          "How did campaign group RecurringInvestment did over the last three months?"
        ],
        "sql": [
          "SELECT\n",
          "  `Year Month`,\n",
          "  MEASURE(`Total Delivered`) AS `Total Delivered`,\n",
          "  MEASURE(`Open Rate`) AS `Open Rate`,\n",
          "  MEASURE(`Click Rate`) AS `Click Rate`,\n",
          "  MEASURE(`Avg Emails Per User`) AS `Avg Emails Per User`\n",
          "\n",
          "FROM\n",
          "  main.bi_output_stg.mvg_marketing_automation\n",
          "WHERE\n",
          "  `Year Month` >= date_format(ADD_MONTHS(current_date(), -3), 'yyyy-MM')\n",
          "  AND `Campaign Group` = 'RecurringInvestment'\n",
          "GROUP BY\n",
          "  ALL "
        ],
        "usage_guidance": [
          "when asked about a general comparison overview of Campaign Group"
        ]
      }
